  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\nThe bottom sheet spacing is a bit higher compared to the designs.\r\n\r\n<img width=300 src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/19339952/94eab41c-6656-45fd-8c2c-e693575a49f1\" />\r\n\r\n<img width=300 src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/19339952/3a42fe46-4b1c-45b4-9c3e-0c963d896edb\" />\r\n\r\n<img width=300 src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/19339952/8d0c2f7e-cdb7-4ad7-b237-b0cbbca72c07\" />\r\n\r\n#### NOTE: This affects all the sheets such as the reaction bottom sheet, documentation bottom sheet, ...etc.\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nThe bottom spacing of the bottom sheet should match the design (should be using the bottom safe area height of the device)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Open Status\r\n2. Long press on any message or community to open the bottom sheet\r\n3. Check the bottom spacing\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly [08/10]\r\n- Operating System: iOS\r\n\r\n",
